					<li class="mb-[0.35rem] text-doc-muted"><strong class="text-doc-text">Spacing scale:</strong> Named scale (e.g. xs, sm, md, lg, xl) with values; usage (padding, margins, gaps).</li>
					<li class="mb-[0.35rem] text-doc-muted"><strong class="text-doc-text">Grid:</strong> Column count, gutter, margin; breakpoints and when the grid changes.</li>
					<li class="mb-[0.35rem] text-doc-muted"><strong class="text-doc-text">Breakpoints:</strong> Named breakpoints (e.g. sm, md, lg, xl) and what they represent (device / viewport intent).</li>
