					<li class="mb-[0.35rem] text-doc-muted"><strong class="text-doc-text">Easing:</strong> Standard curves (ease-in, ease-out, ease-in-out, custom) and use cases.</li>
					<li class="mb-[0.35rem] text-doc-muted"><strong class="text-doc-text">Principles:</strong> When we animate (feedback, focus, transition) and when we don't.</li>
				</ul>

				<h3 id="iconography" class="text-base  mt-6 mb-2 text-doc-text">2.5 Iconography</h3>
